45 of Brownfields Property under G.S. 130A-310.35 is entitled to the partial exclusion provided by
46 this section for the first five taxable years beginning after completion of qualifying improvements
47 made after the later of July 1, 2000, or the date of the upon which the Department of
48 Environmental Quality provides written confirmation that the prospective developer of that land
49 and the proposed improvements are eligible to receive a brownfields agreement. After property
50 has qualified for the exclusion provided by this section, the assessor for the county in which the
