24 WASTEWATER PROJECTS
25 SECTION 6. G.S. 159G-20(21) reads as rewritten:
26 "(21) Targeted interest rate project. – Either of the following types of projects:
27 a. A project that is awarded a loan from the Drinking Water Reserve or
28 the Wastewater Reserve based on affordability.
29 b. A project that is awarded a loan from the CWSRF or the DWSRF and
30 is in a category for which the Department or federal law encourages a
